P_HTM[2642]="*garukaṃ āpattiṃ jānāti,**They know what is a serious offense.*";
P_HTM[2643]="*ubhayāni kho panassa pātimokkhāni vitthārena svāgatāni honti suvibhattāni suppavattīni suvinicchitāni suttaso anubyañjanaso,**Both monastic codes have been passed down to them in detail, well analyzed, well mastered, well judged in both the rules and accompanying material.*";
P_HTM[2644]="*catunnaṃ jhānānaṃ … pe … akasiralābhī,**They get the four absorptions—blissful meditations in the present life that belong to the higher mind—when they want, without trouble or difficulty.*";
