P_HTM[2652]="*anāpattiṃ jānāti,**They know what is not an offense.*";
P_HTM[2653]="*lahukaṃ āpattiṃ jānāti,**They know what is a light offense.*";
P_HTM[2654]="*garukaṃ āpattiṃ jānāti,**They know what is a serious offense.*";
