P_HTM[2659]="*Sattamaṃ.* **";
P_HTM[2660]="*8. Catutthavinayadharasobhanasuttaṃ**Shines as an Expert in the Monastic Law (4th)*";
P_HTM[2661]="*“Sattahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato vinayadharo sobhati.**“Mendicants, a mendicant with seven qualities shines as an expert in the monastic law.*";
P_HTM[2662]="*Katamehi sattahi?**What seven?*";
